import { Component, Input } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-not-found', templateUrl: './not-found.component.html', styleUrls: ['./not-found.component.css'] }) export class NotFoundComponent { @Input() visible = false @Input() notFoundMessage = ' Notting Found' @Input() notFoundText = 'Reset' @Input() notFoundLink = '/' }
